<div id="content" class="col620">


	<div class="post-1127 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-generation-gap category-kink-events category-my-videos category-politics-of-sex category-vanilla-life tag-adultism tag-kfadc tag-kinkforall clear" id="post-1127">
